discussion.content:
The correct Answer is No-No-No;
In Microsoft Teams, private channels are only visible to the members of that channel and are not visible to the owner or administrators of the team. However, the owner or administrators can see the members of the
 private channel by going to the channel's settings and selecting "Manage members."
